Class UserDatabase

java.lang.Object
database.Database
database.UserDatabase
All Implemented Interfaces:
iDatabase
Direct Known Subclasses:
StaffDatabase, StudentDatabase
public class UserDatabase extends Database
This class represents a generic user database for managing user records in an Excel file. It extends the Database class and provides common methods for querying and manipulating user data.
Author:
weiya
